{"tid":1575262,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"921 台灣大地震20周年 不如Connect下台灣","createTime":"2019-09-16T18:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T00:34:05.000Z","uid":180745,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"faee0fad561dde70662304de66902c703423555b","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"可能大家四川/唐山大地震新聞睇得多<br />\n但台灣廿年前 1999既921大地震<br />\n香港人 特別係後生一代 可能唔係好知<br />\n<br />\n呢個對佢地黎講係一單歷史性大災難<br />\n大家身為時不時去台灣旅行既香港人<br />\n除左食下台灣夜市野 j下台妹外<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如一齊關心下同為繁體地區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且一直聲援我地既台灣<br />\n仲記唔記得佢地之前眾籌左好多頭盔比我地呀！<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇左某位巴打既post<br />\n提議話不如整個紀念活動<br />\n巴絲們集思廣益一下 可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n921台灣大地震20週年<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ebzkxT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ebzkxT</a><br />\n - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">而且今年既921咁岩係星期六！</span><br />\n<br />\n二樓會放有關921既資料比大家睇下"},{"pid":"b9011c93641459c929ba262b2ee114cb87da3e44","tid":1575262,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">星期三有大綱睇</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=3ad9a75d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=e2525a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"9a9f3ddce50949553edd9fa64bb94a55811ed638","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPErmi2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPErmi2.jpg&h=826ef080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n921大地震，又稱集集大地震，是1999年9月21日上午1時47分15.9秒（當地時間）發生於臺灣中部山區的逆斷層型地震，造成臺灣全島均感受到嚴重搖晃，共持續約102秒，乃臺灣自二戰後傷亡損失最大的自然災害。<br />\n<br />\n此地震造成2,415人死亡，29人失蹤，11,305人受傷，51,711間房屋全倒，53,768間房屋半倒。不但人員傷亡慘重，也震毀許多道路與橋樑等交通設施、堰壩及堤防等水利設施，以及電力設備、維生管線、工業設施、醫院設施、學校等公共設施，更引發大規模的山崩與土壤液化災害，其中又以台灣中部受災最為嚴重。臺灣鐵路管理局西部幹線一度全面停駛，亦有多數客運公司暫時停駛。<br />\n<br />\n為悼念地震逝去的民眾與警惕自然災害的威脅，中央政府於2000年訂立每年9月21日為「國家防災日」，並舉行地震演習，以求災害來臨時能做好防護措施，將傷亡的可能降至最低。<br />\n<br />\n當時各地最大震度如下：<br />\n震度7：南投魚池<br />\n震度6：雲林古坑、台中市、嘉義阿里山<br />\n震度5：嘉義市、台中德基、花蓮西林、苗栗鯉魚潭、花蓮市、高雄桃源、台南佳里、宜蘭南山、新竹竹北、台東利稻、宜蘭市<br />\n震度4：桃園三光、台東市、屏東縣九如、澎湖縣馬公、台北市、高雄市、台北五分山<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmv93yY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqmv93yY.jpg&h=66fca91e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空拍台北松山區的東星大樓(松山賓館)，東星大樓是台北最嚴重的災區，當時九二一地震後，大樓各層出現嚴重擠壓，共造成 87人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vgo370E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvgo370E.jpg&h=1abedb53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中部災區受到影響最大，圖為當時雲林縣當地倒塌的大樓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptNAeFF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptNAeFF.jpg&h=7ebccd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南投名間鄉距離震央相當近，可見整座大樓倒塌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2EGad0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2EGad0.jpg&h=4cc1e1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1999年9月23日，空拍受災嚴重的南投埔里地區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEhP3y1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEhP3y1.jpg&h=c31cc94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新莊的「博士的家」有 3棟大樓倒塌， 45人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VJgJoyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJgJoyY.jpg&h=530dc50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時救災和善後的人員，有大部份來自國軍。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdju3yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcdju3yX.jpg&h=7f5f70fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救難人員在不斷冒出沙塵的東星大樓外搶救傷患。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/dq.yam.com/amp/post.php%3fid=4685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fdq.yam.com%2Famp%2Fpost.php%253fid%3D4685&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rQ5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=86291598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/dq.yam.com/amp/post.php%3fid=4685</a><br />\n有更加多圖睇 當時有來自世界各地既醫療救護員幫手救災"},{"pid":"1a6d1ed84bce4fea240c2fdcfbd4709ffacd97f7","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:58:33.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"065bd1a539eb3ad651707bd6cf8bc669605afaa8","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:58:46.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9343c49d38b749291efb593f5dab22a4c4fe4dfd","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced807e402ad26f42344713c0ff0bfbd09d98ed8","tid":1575262,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:59:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地點可以唔支持係美國既香港義士</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575249</a>"},{"pid":"d0ecde17d4382d87b2c9103271ebc8456fb52f2a","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T18:59:32.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"70b5e77d195f4eee2709c0185836cc575608e67d","tid":1575262,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T19:00:18.000Z","msg":"幾好！<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地點可以唔支持係美國既香港義士</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1575249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1575249</a>"},{"pid":"443db1642e97b6da2fd374e8a2c90fc010afb458","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"5/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4eb8ed8dc87c3e463949fe62107e397c129e00","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T19:00:58.000Z","msg":"6/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />connect台灣"},{"pid":"c74419fe9d15eeac68afb1be813f6a6b64b29282","tid":1575262,"uid":180745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T19:01:51.000Z","msg":"7/10 比呂麗巴搶左二樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec1a6f198a7ee751c683ba6f6ce5b7482